lead_paragraph: Successful auto racing team owner Carl Haas, a former business partner with the late Hollywood actor Paul Newman, has died at the age of 86, his official website (www.haasauto.com) reported on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: Iconic Team Owner Carl Haas Dies at 86
